Uses of Package
xmlElements

Packages that use xmlElements
server The package server contains the server REST with his services and the publisher to propose those services online. 
xmlElements The package xmlElements contains all the classes that can be marshalled by JaxB in our project, ie : The different response from the APIs (Nominatim, Overpass) The request and the query format for the services of our server (smallestCommonPath, geoScalePathsInArea) the class GeoScalePath that can also be marshalled.
